Successfully.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;2. After that I have created&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/group.sap-build-apps-process-trigger.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Create a Sales Order App Using SAP Build Apps&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;from SAP Build&amp;nbsp;Successfully.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;3. When I try to acccess from Build App Preview getting &lt;STRONG&gt;above destination issue.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rami_reddy4_0-1742196228995.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/238410i447EB96BE4600B44/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="rami_reddy4_0-1742196228995.png" alt="rami_reddy4_0-1742196228995.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Destination&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rami_reddy4_0-1742196089771.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/238409i3078B9C96A9D576A/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="rami_reddy4_0-1742196089771.png" alt="rami_reddy4_0-1742196089771.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;4. As per turorial it will work like this.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rami_reddy4_2-1742195413539.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/238404iA6B9A41FF6BBD8ED/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="rami_reddy4_2-1742195413539.png" alt="rami_reddy4_2-1742195413539.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Regards,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;