    <content>&lt;P&gt;Builders,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I'm encountering an issue while setting up a detail page using a REST API. I've configured a Data Variable that relies on a Page Parameter passed from the previous page to populate a Query Parameter for the API.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The API functions correctly in Postman, supporting all CRUD operations. Specifically, retrieving a single entry via GET requires a URL like:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;PRE&gt;https://*********.accounts.ondemand.com/scim/Users/62f75cbf-0b3a-40b6-9b326-e8c203426&lt;/PRE&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;P&gt;However, when Build Apps constructs the URL, it appends ?0=, resulting in:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Mark112358_1-1744035645093.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/247704iA83BE1FB9EE4B35B/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Mark112358_1-1744035645093.png" alt="Mark112358_1-1744035645093.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;P&gt;This additional ?0= seems to be causing the API to return all records instead of the specific record identified by the Page Parameter. I've confirmed this behavior by manually constructing the same URL in Postman.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;My Questions:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Is there a workaround to prevent Build Apps from appending ?0= to the URL?&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Alternatively, are there other methods to filter the results on the detail page to display the correct record, given that this is a REST API (not OData)?&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;&lt;P&gt;I've observed that most detail page examples utilize OData, which might have different handling. Any insights or suggestions would be greatly appreciated.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/sap-build-apps-rest-api-detail-page-unexpected-0-query-parameter-issue/qaq-p/14068571"/>
    <published>2025-04-07T16:24:59.805000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
